description: This spacious, thoughtfully designed 2+ bed, 3 bath condo offering 2,000+ sq ft of flexible living space with stunning water views from the dining area and private back deck is truly one of a kind. Recently updated kitchen, expansive finished basement with a full bath—ideal as a guest suite, playroom, or multipurpose area. Primary suite features a steam shower and full size bathtub. Includes a garage parking spot with storage and additional driveway space- perfect for snowy days or street cleaning hours. Recently installed security system and new custom built front door. Surrounded by property improvements and the Thomas Park renovation, this home is a great long-term investment opportunity.
